<inglise> Commission Regulation (EC) No 2357/2000 of 24 October 2000 amending Regulation (EC) No 174/1999 laying down special detailed rules for the application of Council Regulation (EEC) No 804/68 as regards export licences and export refunds in the case of milk and milk products </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 2357/2000, millega muudetakse m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 174/1999, millega kehtestatakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 804/68 rakendamise &uuml;ksikasjalikud erieeskirjad piima ja piimatoodete ekspordilitsentside ja -toetuste kohta 24. oktoober 2000 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EC) No 1255/1999 of 17 May 1999 on the common organisation of the market in milk and milk products(1), as last amended by Regulation (EC) No 1670/2000(2), and in particular Article 31(14) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 17. mai 1999. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (E&Uuml;) nr 1255/1999 piima- ja piimatooteturu &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, (1) viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1670/2000, (2) eriti selle artikli 31 l&otilde;iget 14, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> (1) Under Article 5(1) of Commission Regulation (EC) No 1291/2000(3), which is to apply from 1 October 2000, the possibility of using export licences with advance fixing of the refund for supplies to armed forces as referred to in Article 36(1) (c) of Commission Regulation (EC) No 800/1999(4), as amended by Regulation (EC) No 1557/2000(5), will cease. In view of the economic significance of such supplies for the milk sector, a derogation should be granted from Article 5(1) of Regulation (EC) No 1291/2000 so as to re-establish without delay the possibility of fixing the refund for such supplies of milk products in advance. </inglise>
<eesti> 1) alates 1. oktoobrist 2000 kohaldatava komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1291/2000 (3) artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 alusel kaob v&otilde;imalus kasutada komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 800/1999 (4) (muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (E&Uuml;) nr 1557/2000 (5)) artikli 36 l&otilde;ike 1 punktis c osutatud toetuse eelkinnitusega ekspordilitsentse tarnimisel relvaj&otilde;ududele; pidades silmas selliste tarnete majanduslikku t&auml;htsust piimasektorile, tuleks ette n&auml;ha erand m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 1291/2000 artikli 5 l&otilde;ikest 1, et viivitamatult kehtestada j&auml;llev&otilde;imalus selliste piimatoodete tarnimisel toetust eelnevalt kinnitada; </eesti>
<inglise> (2) The measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Milk and Milk Products, </inglise>
<eesti> 2) k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las piima- ja piimatooteturu korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> In Article 2 of Commission Regulation (EC) No 174/1999(6), the following paragraph is added after the first paragraph: "However, by derogation from the first paragraph, an export licence with advance fixing of the refund may be used to grant a refund for exports of milk products as referred to in Article 36(1) (c) of Regulation (EC) No 800/1999. " </inglise>
<eesti> Komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 174/1999 (6) artiklis 2 lisatakse esimese l&otilde;igu j&auml;rele j&auml;rgmine l&otilde;ik: "Erandina esimesest l&otilde;igust v&otilde;ib toetuse eelkinnitusega ekspordilitsentsi kasutada m&auml;&auml;ruse (E&Uuml;) nr 800/1999 artikli 36 l&otilde;ike 1 punktis c osutatud piimatoodete puhul eksporditoetuse andmisel. " </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub j&auml;rgmisel p&auml;eval p&auml;rast Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas avaldamist. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 24 October 2000. </inglise>
